name: ObjectGraphIteratorTest
description: Unit tests for the ObjectGraphIterator class, which is used to iterate over a graph of objects.

nested_classes.name: Branch
nested_classes.description: Internal class representing a branch in a tree structure.

nested_classes.name: Forest

nested_classes.name: Leaf
nested_classes.description: Internal class representing a leaf in a tree structure.

nested_classes.name: LeafFinder
nested_classes.description: Internal class implementing Transformer to find leaves in a forest.

nested_classes.name: Tree
nested_classes.description: Internal class representing a tree containing multiple branches.
